examples.en: He had many absences from work.
Her work involved repeated absences from home.
His frequent absences ended up costing him his job.
His frequent absences from home caused his marriage to unravel.
His long absences didn't help matters (=made the situation worse).
His boss suspected him of malingering because of his frequent absences from work.
A string of absences from this course will be seen as denotative of the student's lack of interest in it.
The principal connived at all the school absences that were recorded on the day of the city's celebration of its Super Bowl victory.
